<h2>About DJ R QUB</h2>

<p>
DJ R QUB is a Kenyan DJ and the founder of R QUB STUDIOZ ENTERTAINMENT.
Known for energetic mixes and creative remixes, DJ R QUB blends genres
including dancehall, soul, Afrobeat and club hits to create unforgettable
music experiences.

Based in Nairobi, Kenya, he has built a growing audience through his
signature mix series "The Evening Call" and multiple themed DJ sessions.

With the motto "Mziki Bila Limit" (Music Without Limits), DJ R QUB aims
to take his sound to international stages while delivering powerful
performances for clubs, festivals, private events and global audiences.

Bookings are open worldwide.
</p>

